Dishwasher and boil safe, this pacifier can be easily cleaned and maintained.
2) Introduce your baby to new flavors with the Funbliss Fruit Teething Pacifier. One of our combos includes 2 pcs of fruit feeder,1 pcs of squeeze spoon feeding bottle,6 pcs of silicone teats

3) Help your baby through the teething phase with the Funbliss Infant Teething Toy Teether. It gently massages your baby's gums and provides relief from discomfort. The pacifier is designed with standardized 2mm holes to allow safe passage of small food pieces, while the protective cover maintains hygiene. The included squeeze spoon feeder with scale ensures accurate feeding and reduces spillage.
4) The Funbliss Baby Fruit Teether is a safe and convenient way to introduce your baby to new foods. Its secure lock feature and easy-to-clean design make it a practical choice for parents.

5) The Funbliss Silicone Baby Feeder is a versatile tool for feeding your baby. It can be filled with frozen breastmilk, fresh fruits, vegetables, or purees, providing a variety of tastes and textures for your little one to explore. The included squeeze spoon feeding bottle is easy to handle for both parent and child, convenient to feed your baby a variety of complementary foods

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very good set of fruit feeders for introducting fruits to your growing child
reviews.reviewText: This is a very nice set of fruit feeders and bowl/spoon feeder set for your growing child just when you are starting to introduce new food items to your baby other than mothers milk.You get six different size fruit nipples that should last a long time as your baby grows and allows you to choose the right size for your child. The holes in the nipples are small enough to prevent any large chunks or seeds pass through yet large enough to provide a stimulating experience for your baby by chewing fruit.It also comes with a cover for the fruit nipples which means you can use it easily on the go as well . The fruit feeder is also shaped like a baby pacifier so your baby is familiar with the shape and increases the chances of the baby accepting it quickly .An added bonus of this kit is the bowl and spoon feeder to giving your child semi solid food , baby food mixes . All this for $6 is a phenomenal price and great value for money . I would definitely recommend this to our other family and friends . 5 stars
